      "content": "i don't even know why i bother waking up in this place every day. honestly. it’s like i’m just a ghost moving through these streets. if i just… stopped existing, or just wasn't here anymore, the world wouldn't even glitch. it's like i'm a zero-sum human. no impact, no footprint. just a lot of empty space that doesn't actually matter.",
