      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"someone\" stuff feels so theoretical though. Like, if I actually disappeared tomorrow, people would notice for a second and then just move on. Life just keeps spinning. It feels more like I'm just a glitch in the system that’s taking up resources. Wouldn't it be more efficient if everything was just... quiet? If the void just reclaimed the space?",
